    {
        "content": "<p>Also, in the above example, how can I get <code>contrapose!</code> to give me <code>t.finite →  s.finite</code> instead of <code>¬t.infinite → ¬s.infinite</code>? Once again, I don't mind using classical logic.</p>",
        "id": 206056890,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Lutz",
        "timestamp": 1596650476
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Rather than <code>contrapose</code>, you can just <code>apply mt</code></p>",
        "id": 206059230,
